item.title: Dumb Ways to Die 2 the Games
item.description: Dumb Ways to Die is back with a bigger and better sequel to the original. In Dumb Ways To Die 2 - The Games, now you can access various maps and locations to try out even more fun and dangerous challenges. Collect tokens to unlock different aspects of the city, while complete mini challenges perfectly (or imperfectly, depending on how you play). Score points to keep your ranking high. Play in cool locations such as Adrenaland, Drown Town, Dumbest of the Dumb, and Freezerville.
